{"type": "article", "id": 22250, "title": "带配件的木质书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-15T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113121oaTF0xAROPK4N1g3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组木质书架上面带有两个小配件，一个是波浪式的木质图案，带有清晰的木纹，另一个带有黑白迷彩纹的圆片，是更加现代的图案。它们都可以在架子上左右滑动，与原本的方框架子构成明显的对比，也有装饰的功能，很特别。也是维也纳设计师 Robert Stadler 想要将书架做有趣的尝试。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113120f5tRxYsIuK4g6A8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071131200NQp9klWAL2OMY7X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113120x5iGu3OeTRBWdIP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113121TWOF0BP5y2d4pojw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}